{
  "texts": [
    "d. Transforming sketches into photographs in color.",
    "3CycleGAN, TripleGAN [73], and DiscoGAN [74] are the most popular versions utilised to accomplish this goal.",
    "featured CycleGAN and further neural machine translation examples, including converting pictures to artworks and a horse from a zebra., and summer to winter photos.",
    "Wang et al.",
    "outlined a technique for semantic image-tophoto translations using conditional GANs."
  ]
